response.original_title: NJPW Road To Power Struggle 2017: Day 9
response.overview: On October 29, 2017, Korakuen Hall in Tokyo hosted Day 9 of NJPW Road To Power Struggle 2017, broadcast on Samurai! TV.  The main event featured Suzuki-gun (Taichi & TAKA Michinoku) vs ACH & Ryusuke Taguchi.  The card also featured Los Ingobernables de Japon (BUSHI, EVIL, Hiromu Takahashi, SANADA & Tetsuya Naito) vs CHAOS (Kazuchika Okada, Rocky Romero, SHO, Tomohiro Ishii & YOH).  Other wrestlers on the show include Dragon Lee, Hiroshi Tanahashi and Kota Ibushi, and more!
response.title: NJPW Road To Power Struggle 2017: Day 9
